+# MOXI Phase 30 Hermes Config Schema Overlay
+
+Technical path source: https://github.com/LUTAO581314/hermes-
+
+This overlay note documents the BaiLongma-side work required after Hermes
+runtime Phase 30.
+
+BaiLongma should proxy these Hermes runtime endpoints:
+
+- `GET /config/schema`
+- `POST /config/update`
+
+Brain UI settings should render the returned schema dynamically instead of
+hard-coding model, search, media, and performance fields.
+
+Required UI behavior:
+
+- Group fields by schema group.
+- Render text, url, int, bool, select, and secret field types.
+- For secret fields, show configured state only.
+- Empty secret inputs must keep the existing secret.
+- POST only changed fields to `/config/update`.
+- Refresh `/config/schema`, `/health`, `/capabilities`, and `/performance`
+  after save.
+- Show validation errors returned by Hermes instead of silently failing.
+
+Do not store raw API keys in localStorage, browser events, chat logs, or public
+job records.
